---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import { BRAND } from '../lib/siteConfig';
---

<LandingLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 md:py-40">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-16">About</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-600 space-y-8 leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-700 font-normal leading-relaxed">
        {BRAND.PREFIX}<span class="text-red-600 font-bold">{BRAND.HIGHLIGHT}</span>{BRAND.SUFFIX} is a small, independent tool for fertility awareness.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg">
        It exists for one simple reason:<br/>
        to make it easier to understand where you are in your cycle, without turning it into a complicated app or a data-hungry service.
      </p>


      <p class="text-lg">
        We wanted something that is:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-3 text-lg">
        <li>Simple to use</li>
        <li>Calm and respectful</li>
        <li>Focused on one job</li>
        <li>Private by default</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg">
        The app is based on well-known fertility awareness ideas (like tracking cycle length, temperature, and daily signs), but it keeps things intentionally simple.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg">
        This is not a social app.<br/>
        This is not a content platform.<br/>
        This is not trying to keep you "engaged".
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg font-medium">
        It's just a tool.
      </p>

      <p class="pt-12 border-t border-slate-100 mt-16 text-lg">
        {BRAND.PREFIX}<span class="text-red-600 font-bold">{BRAND.HIGHLIGHT}</span>{BRAND.SUFFIX} is built and maintained by a small independent team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>
